edu.ncsu.csc216.get_outdoors

Class GetOutdoorsManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • edu.ncsu.csc216.get_outdoors.GetOutdoorsManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Observer

    public class GetOutdoorsManager
extends java.util.Observable
implements java.util.Observer
    The main class for the GetOutdoors tools. Holds references to the top-level data structures and acts as the controller between the model and the GUI presentation view.
    Author:
    Jessica Young Schmidt, Your Name Here

    • Constructor Detail

      • GetOutdoorsManager

        public GetOutdoorsManager()
        Constructs the GetOutdoorsManager by doing the following: 1. Constructs the trailLists array with at least three elements. 2. Constructs a new ActivityList. The GetOutdoorsManager instance should be an Observer of the ActivityList. 3. Constructs a new ParkList. The GetOutdoorsManager instance should be an Observer of the ParkList. 4. changed should be set to false.
